"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## Understanding Gauges\\n\\n# The gauge system\\n\\nOn Curve Finance, the inflation is going to users who provide liquidity. This usage is measured with gauges. The liquidity gauge measures how much a user is providing in liquidity.\\n\\nThe liquidity gauge measures how many dollars you have provided in a Curve pool. Each Curve pool has its own liquidity gauge where you can stake your liquidity provider tokens\\n\\n# The weight system\\n\\nEach gauge also has a weight and a type. Those weights represent how much of the daily CRV inflation will be received by the liquidity gauge.\\n\\n# The DAO\\n\\nThe weight systems allow the Curve DAO to dictate where the CRV inflation should go. You can vote at this address: <https://dao.curve.fi/gaugeweight>\\n\\nBy doing so, you can put your voting power towards the liquidity gauge (or pool) you think should receive the most CRV.\\n\\n## Gauge Weight Voting\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/NdJO16jRL-HuXtu1XacjP.png?height=827&width=896)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/z0ZFK4twp5l6Dtjhz8Ovg.png?height=711&width=876)\\n\\nYou can vote for gauge weight with your veCRV tokens(locked CRV tokens in [Locker](https://dao.curve.fi/locker)). Gauge weights are used to determine how much CRV does each pool get\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/NM7XQJeorptEHHbIgQC6V.png?height=751&width=944)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7y8FE_xhfj1qlD8SWV1Fn.png?height=408&width=946)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2s4xvLdfuK9mNHzAR0MmK.png?height=257&width=595)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LvsSQrIgbdcwMbOudt91K.png?height=594&width=1001)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KEyIPL4rK1cgE_rAypLcG.png?height=550&width=963)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8CFwSJexHu2ovOxbu-B_C.png?height=733&width=992)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zSMe1HOhtF_Ek4WriTcTj.png?height=576&width=887)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pQhhPP-EkvtR6Gf9AS_Vh.png?height=718&width=898)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641524889,\"title\":\"Curve 学习\"},\"digest\":\"TdDleXPB0zgCUozp4NMLOz7Gz1SmWEAveHxcqokfKEU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd8E93E06a84581c10DC1F9F60ec91f0F38994f1b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"a_dLERd4Cdhgh6ry9Yrs5OcBF3DZRTMLU7lo2MyzU9U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MrUMilaNceSEdYCTf-Dl1YVGchaRIPZPad-TuPvv354\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"oC7eHHcbvs7uA4FxvH4kqqLI23Xo5HIwHi5TLikoLGVoQ_l4i-MGHnouYdzwxcqmQRqDDYt2328Jd5tfUdQKUg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x08a7d98f6049e83344439b1e6456022e902321dd36a860487d9259b6b59ae18e5371ddb10a61a785172c817e9acf134fe8046ce86d14e87ad0ce4dc0b4b331751b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"a_dLERd4Cdhgh6ry9Yrs5OcBF3DZRTMLU7lo2MyzU9U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MrUMilaNceSEdYCTf-Dl1YVGchaRIPZPad-TuPvv354\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"lfFkm9O2_N8rkdg07KV9frqUGR9si9UHTJFmmOGexA8\"}"